PN,36501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,FA grandfather who developed a brain
OL,7,Faneurysm has been spared invasive
OL,8,Fsurgery after doctors carried out a
OL,9,Fpioneering procedure through his eye
OL,10,Fsocket.
OL,12,FAndrew Wood, 61, faced a craniotomy `
OL,13,Fwhere surgeons remove part of the
OL,14,Fskull to get to the affected area `
OL,15,Fafter finding out he had swelling on
OL,16,Fthe brain.
OL,18,FBut experts at Leeds Teaching
OL,19,FHospitals NHS Trust performed a
OL,20,Fkeyhole operation though the eye
OL,21,Fsocket in a UK first.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,FMr Wood, a builder, was in hospital
OL,7,Ffor just a single night and returned
OL,8,Fto work just a few weeks after the
OL,9,Foperation in February.
OL,11,FMr Wood added: "It has been perfect
OL,12,Fsince, I've had no double vision, no
OL,13,Fpain, I'm back at work ` I just have
OL,14,Fto watch out that I don't hit myself
OL,15,Fwith a two by four.
OL,17,F"Thanks to the skill of the surgical
OL,18,Fteam, I've been given a second chance.
OL,26,@sD@POU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,F"I'm really grateful for their
OL,7,Fkindness and expertise ` they are an
OL,8,Foutstanding team. I'm proud to have
OL,9,Fbeen part of such an important
OL,10,Fprocedure and I'm amazed at how
OL,11,Fquickly I recovered and returned home."
OL,13,FMr Wood was found to have an aneurysm
OL,14,Fwhile being scanned for a separate
OL,15,Fmedical issue last spring.
OL,17,FHe was told about the pioneering
OL,18,Ftechnique for treating it by
OL,19,Fconsultant neurosurgeon Asim Sheikh.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,FSurgeons made a "tiny" incision at the
OL,7,Fside of Mr Wood's eye and a cut on the
OL,8,Fouter wall of the eye socket to gain
OL,9,Faccess to the aneurysm.
OL,11,FThe same team had performed a similar
OL,12,Foperation in 2024 when they removed a
OL,13,Fbrain tumour through a patient's eye
OL,14,Fsocket ` another UK-first.
OL,16,FMr Sheikh said that Mr Wood "got the
OL,17,Fbest of both worlds" by having the
OL,18,Fsurgery.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@VO]xD@]OUyD@TO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,FHe said: "As we gained more
OL,7,Fexperience, we realised that the same
OL,8,Fapproach could be used to access other
OL,9,Fpathologies in the similar area ` in
OL,10,FAndrew's case a brain aneurysm.
OL,12,F"His aneurysm happened to be in a very
OL,13,Feasily accessible area, which would
OL,14,Fhave been perfect for this technique.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,F"And that means he can get the best of
OL,7,Fboth worlds of the surgical treatment
OL,8,Fof his aneurysm ` the best possible,
OL,9,Fdurable cure for his aneurysm while
OL,10,Fcutting down on the drawbacks of
OL,11,Fhaving surgery including big cuts and
OL,12,Fscars, big incisions on the head and
OL,13,Falso the morbidity of going through
OL,14,Fthe brain and retracting the brain `
OL,15,Fall that is completely taken away by
OL,16,Fthis minimal access surgery."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,FTo prepare for the procedure,
OL,7,Fbiomechanical engineers from the
OL,8,Fhospital created a bespoke 3D printed
OL,9,Fmodel of Mr Wood's eye socket and
OL,10,Fsurrounding skull base anatomy as well
OL,11,Fas the aneurysm.
OL,13,FThis allowed Mr Sheikh and consultant
OL,14,Fmaxillofacial surgeon Jiten Parmar to
OL,15,Fprepare and rehearse the procedure,
OL,16,Ftailored specifically to Mr Wood's
OL,17,Fanatomy.
OL,19,FMr Sheikh said the operation is a
OL,20,F"significant step forward in minimally
OL,21,Finvasive brain surgery in the UK".
OL,26,@|D@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,FHe added: "It was easily accessible
OL,7,Fthrough this approach.
OL,9,F"Traditionally, we would have done a
OL,10,Ftraditional craniotomy, which means
OL,11,Fmaking a big opening in the skull and
OL,12,Freaching it through that to where his
OL,13,Faneurysm was situated between two
OL,14,Fparts of the brain called the frontal
OL,15,Fand temporal.
OL,17,F"So traditionally, you have to split
OL,18,Fthe two halves, pull them apart to get
OL,19,Fto the aneurysm, and then place a
OL,20,Fmetal clip across it.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,F"With this technique, we didn't even
OL,7,Fhave to touch the brain, we didn't
OL,8,Fhave to put any retraction on the
OL,9,Fbrain and we were directly approaching
OL,10,Fthe aneurysm, which meant that the
OL,11,Fmorbidity of the operation itself was
OL,12,Fsubstantially reduced."
OL,14,FMr Parmar added: "This case highlights
OL,15,Fhow working in partnership across
OL,16,Fspecialities, combining decades of
OL,17,Fexperience and working closely with
OL,18,Four engineering team can result in a
OL,19,Fbetter outcome for our patients.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@WO]vD@ROU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779228661
OL,3,CBuilder back to work after brain
OL,4,Csurgery via eye socket
OL,6,F"Most importantly, we achieved a
OL,7,Fbrilliant result for the patient who
OL,8,Fwent home the next day."
OL,10,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,11,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,12,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,13,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,14,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,15,Fbelow...
